# Aseprite Viewer Project Roadmap (Started: 2026-02-12)
Current Version: v33 (Stable) - GitHub Uploaded

## [CURRENT STATUS - v36]
- Hybrid Profile System: Independent Player/NPC management.
- Combat: Max 2-stack combo buffering, Dash cancel support, Step-by-step combo sequence (1-4).
- Movement: Combo-forward movement (1/3 scale of previous speed).
- Camera: Vertical offset slider, Right-drag manual control.
- Playback: Pause(P), Frame Step(O), Speed control([, ]), Refresh(F5).
- Hitbox: Slice data visualization (Hit/Hurt boxes) with persistent key logic (H toggle).
- Watch Mode: Automatic reload on Aseprite file save.
- Juice & VFX: Screen Shake (on Combo 4 & Powerbomb impact), After-images for Dash.
- UI Fix: Resolved Settings scroll-click synchronization bug.

